            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                InPulse is a collaborative platform designed to enhance team communication by providing real-time insights into user activities. With features that show who is online, typing, viewing the chat, or present in the session, InPulse helps teams stay connected and informed during collaborative work. This platform is built for teams and organizations that rely on seamless, real-time interactions to improve productivity and communication efficiency.
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="faq-item">
            <div class="question">
                <span>How to see informations about me and my team?</span>
                <img src="images/icon-chevron-left.svg" style="width: 20px; height: 20px;">
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                To view information about yourself and your team, simply click on the "My Section" button located on the top menu of the site. This will take you to a dedicated area where you can see profiles and details about your team members, as well as your own information. This section is designed to give you a comprehensive overview of who is on your team and their roles.
            </div>
        </li>
