                <span>How to attend a Video Conference?</span>
                <img src="images/icon-chevron-left.svg" style="width: 20px; height: 20px;">
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                After logging into InPulse, you'll be directed to your "Homepage," where you'll find the "Attend a Meeting" button. By clicking this button, you'll be automatically connected to any ongoing video conference. This allows you to join meetings quickly and seamlessly without needing to navigate through multiple steps.
            </div>
        </li>
