                <img src="images/icon-chevron-left.svg" style="width: 20px; height: 20px;">
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                After logging into InPulse, you'll arrive at your "Homepage." To create a video conference, simply click the "Create a Meeting" button. This will instantly set up a new meeting where you can invite participants and begin your session. The process is straightforward, allowing you to start your video conference quickly and efficiently.            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="faq-item">
            <div class="question">
                <span>What is Kanban?</span>
                <img src="images/icon-chevron-left.svg" style="width: 20px; height: 20px;">
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                Kanban is a visual project management tool built into InPulse's Video Conference feature. It provides an organized board where tasks are displayed in columns, representing different stages of a project. With a simple drag-and-drop interface, teams can easily track progress and collaborate more effectively, ensuring a smooth workflow from start to finish.            </div>
